data.description: Welcome to 1300 Forest Drive! This beautiful home is located on the east side of Turlock in an established and quiet neighborhood. As you enter this spacious 1,660 sqft home, you’re instantly greeted with upgraded laminate flooring that opens up to the living room and kitchen. The kitchen features custom herringbone tile backsplash, white quartz countertops, refinished cabinets with new hardware, and recessed lighting. The living room has an inviting brick fireplace and barn doors that lead to a laundry room with custom tile floors. Down the hall, you’ll find 3 bedrooms, including the master suite which features a walk-in closet, subway tile in the bathroom, and upgraded sleek black fixtures. The backyard is perfect for entertaining with a covered patio and in-ground swimming pool with recently upgraded pool equipment. Additionally, this home comes with a full-house reverse-osmosis water softener system. Attached is a two-car garage with RV parking ensures space for all your needs. Nestled in one of Turlock’s finest neighborhoods, and only 5 minutes from excellent schools, including Julien Elementary, Dutcher Middle School, and Turlock High School.
